## Data availability

The tree-ring datasets used in this study were generated from field measurements and are not publicly deposited due to ongoing research activities.

Users can reproduce the analytical workflow using their own tree-ring datasets following the data structure described in this repository.
The required input data structure includes:

- year: calendar year
- lon: longitude
- lat: latitude
- tree-ring chronology: standardized radial growth index (e.g., STD)
- climate variables: temperature, precipitation
- large-scale climate variability indices
